PULOVER.original: ~r~The vans were not pulled over in time.~s~
PULOVER.translated: ~r~未能及时截停所有目标货车。~s~

PULOVER.original: Get back in the ~B~car.
~s~The ~b~vans~S~ are in transit. Find them and pull them over.
PULOVER.translated: ~b~货车~S~都在行驶中。找到并截停它们。

PULOVER.original: ~r~The van was not delivered to the lockup.~s~
PULOVER.translated: ~r~未将目标货车送到指定车库中。~s~

PULOVER.original: ~s~Pull over the ~b~van.
Find a cop car that doesn't have a busted siren.
PULOVER.translated: 找一辆警笛可以正常发声的警车。

PULOVER.original: Lose the wanted before delivering the van.
PULOVER.translated: 在前往车库前摆脱通缉。

PULOVER.original: ~S~Take the van to the ~Y~lockup.
Get closer to the ~b~van.
Lose your wanted level.
Park up and approach the driver's window.
PULOVER.translated: 停车，走到货车驾驶室旁。

PULOVER.original: Get back into the ~b~van.
~s~Find and pull over the ~b~vans~S~ before they reach their destinations.
PULOVER.translated: ~s~在有货车到达其目的地前截停所有~b~货车。~S~

PULOVER.original: ~S~Check out what's in the back of the van.
~s~Stay close to the ~b~van~s~ to make it pull over.
~s~Find and pull over the ~b~van~S~ before it reaches its destination.
PULOVER.translated: ~s~在货车到达其目的地前截停~b~货车。

PULOVER.original: Pull over the other ~B~vans.
Press ~PAD_LB~ to close van doors.
Stop and search the other vans.
~S~You need a cop car to pull over the vans.
PULOVER.translated: ~S~你需要一辆警车才能截停那些货车。

PULOVER.original: ~S~Find a cop car.
~s~Steal the ~b~van.
Press ~INPUT_VEH_HORN~ to turn on the siren and pull the van over.
~r~The content of the van wasn't checked.~s~
~S~Get out of the van.
~s~Drive to the ~y~lockup.
~R~The van got away.~s~
